data.description: Lovely spacious home on a cul-de-sac. Lot is 63x207. Lot backs up to trees, enjoy the view and privacy. Large eat in Kitchen with breakfast bar, plenty of cabinets plus a pantry, hardwood floors and vaulted ceiling, sliding door exits to deck.  Living Room with vaulted ceiling and fireplace. Home features 4 bedrooms, large master bedroom with walk-in closet. Beautiful master bath with columns, separate shower and double sinks. Finished lower level offers 4th bedroom and 3rd bathroom. Family room or possible (5th bedroom) walks out to the patio. All appliances stay. Refrigerator is a 2021. If you have trouble scheduling with Broker Bay Please call me.
